{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 38,
  "title": "第三十八章（論德）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "上德不德，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以有德。"
    },
    {
      "text": "下德不失德，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以無德。"
    },
    {
      "text": "上德無為，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而無以為，"
    },
    {
      "text": "下德為之，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而有以為。"
    },
    {
      "text": "上仁為之，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而無以為，"
    },
    {
      "text": "上義為之，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而有以為。"
    },
    {
      "text": "上禮為之，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而莫之應，"
    },
    {
      "text": "則攘臂而扔之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故失道而後德，"
    },
    {
      "text": "失德而後仁，"
    },
    {
      "text": "失仁而後義，"
    },
    {
      "text": "失義而後禮。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫禮者，忠信之薄，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而亂之首。"
    },
    {
      "text": "前識者道之華，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而愚之始。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以大丈夫處其厚，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不居其薄，"
    },
    {
      "text": "處其實，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不居其華。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故去彼取此。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上德，謂太古無名號之君，德大無上，故言上德也。不德者，言其不以德教民，因循自然，養人性命，其德不見，故言不德也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言其德合於天地，和氣流行，民德以全也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "下德，謂號謚之君，德不及上德，故言下德也。不失德者，其德可見，其功可稱也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以有名號及其身故。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂法道安靜，無所施為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言無以名號為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言為教令，施政事也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言以為己取名號也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上仁謂行仁之君，其仁無上，故言上仁。為之者，為人恩也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "功成事立，無以執為。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "為義以斷割也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "動作以為己，殺人以成威，賊下以自奉也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂上禮之君，其禮無上，故言上禮。為之者，言為禮制度，序威儀也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言禮華盛實衰，飭偽煩多，動則離道，不可應也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言禮煩多不可應，上下忿爭，故攘臂相仍引。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言道衰而德化生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言德衰而仁愛見也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 17,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言仁衰而分義明也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 18,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言義衰則施禮聘，行至帛也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-20",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 19,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言禮廢本治末，忠信日以衰薄。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-21",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 20,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "禮者賤質而貴文，故正直日以少，邪亂日以生。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-22",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 21,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不知而言知為前識，此人失道之實，得道之華。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-23",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 22,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言前識之人，愚闇之倡始也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-24",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 23,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大丈夫謂得道之君也。處其厚者，謂處身於敦樸。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-25",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 24,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不處身違道，為世煩亂也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-26",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 25,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "處忠信也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-27",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 26,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不尚華言也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-28",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 27,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "去彼華薄，取此厚實。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
